                <note rend="inline" type="source">740.00119 ACI/32: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Representative to the French Committee of National Liberation at
                        Algiers</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Wilson</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1943-12-27T20:00:00-04:00"
                            >December 27, 1943—8 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>238. For Reinhardt, your telegram no. 252, December 25, 4 p.m. You are authorized
                    to associate yourself with the extension of the invitation to the Yugoslav and
                    Greek Governments to be represented on the Advisory Council for Italy.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
